        <p>Through this portal, people can create an account, get access and experiment in NITOS FI Facility, which stands for Network Implementation Testbed using Open Source platforms Future Internet Facility.</p>

        
        <p>The main components of NITOS FI facility are:</p>

        <div class = "about-list">
          <ul>

            <li>Two Wi-Fi experimentation testbeds, which consist of powerful nodes (some of them mobile), that also feature multiple wireless interfaces and allow for experimentation with heterogeneous (Wi-Fi, Bluetooth, ZigBee) wireless technologies.</li>

            

            <%= image_tag("IMG_5222_after.jpg", :alt => "photo outdoor", :height => "225", :width => "255") %>

            <%= image_tag("SAM_0626.JPG", :alt => "photo outdoor", :height => "225", :width => "255") %>

            
