            <li>A 4G testbed which consists of WiMAX and LTE Base Stations and the necessary equipment for enabling WiMAX/LTE connectivity to the wireless nodes.</li>

            <li>A software defined radio (SDR) testbed that consists of Universal Software Radio Peripheral (USRP) devices attached to the NITOS wireless nodes.</li>

            <li>A Software Defined Networking (SDN) testbed that consists of multiple OpenFlow technology enabled switches, connected to NITOS nodes, thus enabling experimentation with switching and routing networking protocols.</li>

          </ul>
